l>a</Label><Text>S.C. 2005, c. 9</Text></Footnote></Provision></Order><Body lims:inforce-start-date="2006-10-05" lims:fid="725201" lims:id="725201"><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-10-05" lims:fid="725202" lims:id="725202" level="1"><TitleText>Prescribed Investments</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2024-12-16" lims:enacted-date="2024-12-16" lims:lastAmendedDate="2024-12-16" lims:fid="725203" lims:id="1503265"><MarginalNote lims:inforce-start-date="2024-12-16" lims:enacted-date="2024-12-16" lims:fid="1503266" lims:id="1503266">Permitted investments</MarginalNote><Label>1</Label><Text>For the purposes of paragraph 87(2)(f) of the <XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="F-11.67">First Nations Fiscal Management Act</XRefExternal>, funds in a short-term pooled investment fund may be invested in pooled investment funds established by the Municipal Finance Authority of British Columbia under section 16 of the British Columbia <XRefExternal reference-type="act">Municipal Finance Authority Act</XRefExternal>, R.S.B.C. 1996, c. 325.</Text><HistoricalNote><HistoricalNoteSubItem lims:inforce-start-date="2024-12-16" lims:enacted-date="2024-12-16" lims:fid="1503268" lims:id="1503268" lims:enactId="1502723">SOR/2024-277, s. 2</HistoricalNoteSubItem></HistoricalNote></Section><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-10-05" lims:fid="725205" lims:id="725205" level="1"><TitleText>Coming into Force</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2006-10-05" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-10-05" lims:fid="725206" lims:id="725206" type="transitional"><MarginalNote lims:inforce-start-date="2006-10-05" lims:fid="725207" lims:id="725207">Coming into force</MarginalNote><Label>2</Label><Text>These Regulations come into force on the day on which they are registered.</Text></Section></Body><RecentAmendments><Amendment><AmendmentCitation>SOR/2024-277</AmendmentCitation><AmendmentDate>2024-12-16</AmendmentDate></Amendment></RecentAmendments></Regulation>